; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests balanced virtual postings with multiple commodities.
; When virtual postings involve multiple commodities, the virtual_balance
; is a balance_t and must be handled via map_sorted_amounts.

2024/01/01 Test multi-commodity virtual
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash               $-50.00
    [Budget:EUR]               10 EUR
    [Budget:GBP]                5 GBP
    [Budget:Mix]

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
                   0  Budget
              10 EUR    EUR
               5 GBP    GBP
             -10 EUR
              -5 GBP    Mix
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
